PostgreSQL database with pgAdmin web interface.

## Quick Start

    # .env is generated — update passwords before starting
    docker compose up -d

## Access

* PostgreSQL: localhost:{{ .postgresPort }}
* pgAdmin: http://localhost:{{ .pgadminPort }}

Log in to pgAdmin with the credentials from your .env file.
Connect pgAdmin to the database using the hostname postgres.
